"<C-x><C-F>       : auto-completion filename
"<C-x><C-L>       : auto-completion Line
"<C-x><C-O>       : auto-completion Omni (filetype)
":ls              : open buffer-list
":%s/\%Vxxx/yyy/  : substitut in Visual-Area
